{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_52_02",
  "title": "兵藤雫",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても京都に来てまでアイドルライブに\n行きたいなんて、本当に雫はアイドルが好きだな",
      "startTime": 3.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "むしろ京都だからこそ、アイドルライブに行くべき……\n京都を活動拠点にしているアイドルは沢山いる……",
      "startTime": 12.5023477912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "前から気になってたアイドルも、活動拠点が京都で……\n今まで見に行く機会がなかった……",
      "startTime": 21.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "そのアイドルに、初めて会いに行ける……\n楽しみ過ぎて、興奮が止まらない……！",
      "startTime": 27.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "京都に来ても雫は通常運転だな……\nそういえば、昼間は一人でどこに出かけていたんだ？",
      "startTime": 34.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "夕方のライブまで時間があったから……\nアイドルの無銭ライブをはしごしてた……",
      "startTime": 41,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルライブまでの時間潰しに\nアイドルライブを観てきたのか……",
      "startTime": 46.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "無銭ライブは、無料で観られるライブだけど……\nレベルが低い訳じゃない……むしろ逆……",
      "startTime": 52.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "気軽に観られる分、新規のお客さんが多い……\nアイドルにとっては新規ファンを獲得するチャンス……",
      "startTime": 59.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "だから有料公演に引けを取らないステージをする……\nお試しでアイドルライブを観たい人に、うってつけ……",
      "startTime": 66.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "想像していた京都の楽しみ方とは少し違うが……\n雫が京都旅行を満喫しているようで良かったよ",
      "startTime": 74.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルライブの現場参戦……やっぱり楽しい……\n最近は、あんまりライブに行けてなかったから……",
      "startTime": 82.2333363851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.2000030518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "雫も今やBIG4だからな。特にアイドルライブだと\nバレたら騒ぎになりそうで参加し辛いだろ",
      "startTime": 90.6666697185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.9333363851
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "でもここなら、客席に私がいるとは誰も思わない……\n周囲の目を気にせず、ライブを楽しめる……",
      "startTime": 98.9666697185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.7333363851
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "とはいえ、さすがに一人で行かせるのは心配だからな\n今日は俺もアイドルライブに付き合うよ",
      "startTime": 107.1234506238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.9333363851
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが一緒なら安心……\nはっ、もうこんな時間……急いで行かないと……",
      "startTime": 112.2333363851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと夢見てた京都の推しとの初対面……\n今日は思い切り満喫する……！",
      "startTime": 119.8666697185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_kyoto-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "kyoto-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.5666697185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくの慰安旅行だ\n遠慮なく、思う存分楽しんでくれ",
      "startTime": 124.6333363851,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5766.667175200013,
          "startTime": 130.4000035603
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――アイドルライブが開演して、五分後",
      "startTime": 128.9666656495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.4000035603
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.4000035603
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "はいっ！　はいっ！　はいはいはいはい！\nうおおおお！　さあたーん！　さあたーん！",
      "startTime": 134.0666702271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（雫のやつ、客席の最前列に陣取って）\n（現地のドルオタと一緒に飛び跳ねているぞ）",
      "startTime": 141.4666702271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（予習してきたんだろうな。コールのタイミングが）\n（完璧で、全力で楽しもうという気迫が伝わってくる）",
      "startTime": 148.3000035604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "はぅっ！　今のは見間違いじゃない……\nステージの上から、私を指差してくれた……",
      "startTime": 155.2866343883,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "推しからファンサをもらった……感激……！",
      "startTime": 158.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（こんなにはしゃぐ雫を見るのは久し振りだな）\n（無邪気に、心からライブを楽しんで……）",
      "startTime": 166.4333368938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（客席でこれだけ盛り上がってくれたら）\n（歌っている方も嬉しいだろうな）",
      "startTime": 172.4616054762,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.2333368938
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……ライブ、終わった……\n最高過ぎて、あっという間だった……体感五秒……",
      "startTime": 180.9000035604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 184.4000035604
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "……ん？　会場のスタッフが、こっちに走ってきた……\nえ……何……私……？",
      "startTime": 190.2666702271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 190.2666702271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_52_02-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "今すぐ会場の外に出て行ってほしいって……\n出禁ってこと……ですか？\n",
      "startTime": 201.3244455655,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}